snippet.title: Duke Nukem Xmas 2014 - EDuke32 Mod
snippet.description:
I recorded a few one-liners for this mod, so I thought I'd upload a playthrough of it. Plus, it's Christmas, too. It's a short mod, but these guys did a good job on it. Definitely worth a play!

Mod DB page:
http://www.moddb.com/mods/duke-nukem-xmas-2014

The song, Let it Snow, plays in this map, but I turned the music off just to be safe. You know how YouTube has been lately with copyright. I apologize. 

Merry Christmas!
